					<description><![CDATA[<p>Instagram filters can improve your photos and your marketing in just a few swipes. Here, we're sharing essential rules for using Instagram filters, the most popular filters, and more!</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/06/26/instagram-filters">The Complete Guide to Instagram Filters</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
